and that it never got back to the missus.

06:39.565 --> 06:42.762
<i>- The fuck you talking about?
- You didn't hear the joke about Ginny?</i>

06:43.703 --> 06:46.297
Never mind. Let it die a death.

06:46.539 --> 06:47.904
What joke?

06:49.075 --> 06:51.771
You're better off not hearing it. Trust me.

06:51.978 --> 06:54.674
Fuck that! I demand you tell me, Paulie!

06:55.181 --> 06:58.639
