than we got carpenters.

06:58.718 --> 07:00.345
What's the problem?

07:00.453 --> 07:03.581
The carpenters
are carrying sheetrock and materials.

07:03.656 --> 07:06.955
- We ain't getting what we expected to get.
- Minimally expected.

07:07.026 --> 07:09.119
Let Massarone hire more laborers
off the books.

07:09.195 --> 07:10.662
Nobody's talking to you!

07:11.664 --> 07:13.291
All right, Jesus.

07:20.173 --> 07:21.640
65:35.

07:24.177 --> 07:26.873
